# External Skills Folder

This folder contains skills downloaded from external sources.
Each skill should have its own subfolder with a SKILL.md file.

## Metadata Fields for External Skills

External SKILL.md files should include:
- `source`: Where the skill came from (e.g., "vercel-labs", "anthropic")
- `source-url`: Original URL of the skill

Example:
```yaml
---
name: example-skill
description: An example external skill
version: 1.0.0
source: github
source-url: https://github.com/example/skill
---
```
